*Borbe* su počele. (The fights have started.)
Oni se *borbe* za slobodu. (They are fighting for freedom.)
Učesnici *borbi* su bili veoma hrabri. (Participants of the fights were very brave.)
Niko nije očekivao da će *borbe* biti tako teške. (No one expected the fights to be so difficult.)
Vojnici se spremaju za *borbu*. (Soldiers are preparing for the battle.)